Package: replr
Title: Local HTTP/JSON REPL for R
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Shane", "Lindsay", email = "shane.lindsay@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Launches a local httpuv-based REPL server for evaluating R code and returning results as structured JSON, with Bash/Python/PowerShell clients.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: httpuv, jsonlite, utils, httr, later, tibble
Suggests: testthat, processx
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://github.com/shanelindsay/replr
BugReports: https://github.com/shanelindsay/replr/issues
